description: Creating an everlasting bond is one of the most important ways to maintain a meaningful relationship with kids, especially once they become teenagers.
headline: Creating a Lasting Bond With the Kids
headings: About Me--Tags--How An Open Adoption Can Expand Your Child’s Life--3 Ways To Create A Cool And Cozy Winter Wedding--2 Ways To Save Money On A Casket For A Funeral--Foster Care to Adoption Vs. Private Adoption--Stress-Saving Steps To Take When Adopting A Child
contento: Being a parent is never an easy job. If you aren't spending time being worried about your child's welfare, chances are that you are dealing with an attitude problem of some kind. But there is nothing more rewarding than raising children, and those rewards tend to become most apparent once the kids are grown and raising their own families. Creating an everlasting bond is one of the most important ways to maintain a meaningful relationship with kids, especially once they become teenagers and are looking to make their own way in life. Luckily, I've found lots of techniques to be helpful with raising my own kids throughout the years so I thought I'd pass my experiences in hopes of helping others create a lasting bond with their own kids. I sure hope the information and ideas on this website is helpful for you and your family!

We are a short Uber or cab ride to the Port of Miami, the Miami Airport, or West Palm Beach Airport.--STAY & PLAY-- --FACILITIES--Our facilities include 11 units of suites, studios, and cottages.  Each equipped with a queen size bed, private baths, A/C, flat screen TVs, DVD & VCR players. Our suites and cottages come equipped with full-size kitchens or kitchenettes with toasters, coffee makers and microwaves as well. We have free Wi-Fi in every room and yes, each room comes equipped with it's own sling.--A Sling in every Room--Inn Leather amenities include a heated pool, hot tub, 2 sun decks rest areas, outdoor showers, lockers & much more. Free continental breakfast is served every morning from 8:00 to 10:00 AM .There is also free wireless through out the entire property & free off-street parking. Monthly themed events listed on Facebook, please visit and like us at Facebook  Day Passes available daily 10am - 5pm$10.00

Workers In Sex Employment (WISE) in the ACT Inc. is a community based organization that delivers peer education and support to sex workers and their clients in the ACT.


 
 
 
 




Bookmark this page for future reference




 
 
 
 


WISE has a comprehensive library and information available on issues such as:

 
Sexual Health - Sexually Transmitted Diseases (including HIV/AIDS and Hepatitis); 
Prostitution Laws - in Canberra and interstate;
 
Industrial Issues - Occupational Health & Safety, taxation, superannuation, your rights and responsibilities as a sex worker;
 
Drug & Alcohol issues - safer injecting practices, harm Minimization for drug 
dependent individuals, referral to appropriate services;
 
Referral - we can refer you to other relevant sex worker-friendly services
and professionals;
 
Sex Worker Rights - discrimination, stigma and other issues.


 

We stock condoms, lubricant, dental dams, gloves, massage oils and other tools

of the trade at cost price.




We are also a registered needle exchange
